<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Scary Threatening Site</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #111;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            animation: flicker 1.5s infinite alternate;
        }
        @keyframes flicker {
            0% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.7; }
            100% { opacity: 1; }
        }
        img {
            width: 300px;
            height: auto;
            border: 5px solid #ff0000;
            margin: 20px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
            filter: grayscale(100%) brightness(0.7);
        }
        img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            filter: none;
        }
        .caption {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #ff0000;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
            animation: shake 0.5s infinite alternate;
        }
        @keyframes shake {
            0% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-5deg); }
        }
        .time-warning {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #ff0000;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="nigga1.jpg" alt="Scary Image 1">
        <img src="nigga2.jpg" alt="Scary Image 2">
        <div class="caption">نكمك يا عطاي تناكت عليك قضية وقت برك</div>
        <div class="time-warning">You'll be fucked in 24 hours!</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
